lations. The calculated T_c(d_F)\ndependences are compared with existing experimental data for Fe/Nb/Fe trilayers\nand Nb/Co multilayers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Dec 2001 16:44:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2002 21:12:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2003 19:50:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-31"}
